DOM--(Documnet object model) repreents the web page as a tree like sturtuer, which alloews js.
     to dynamically access and manipulsationnthe content and struture of a web page.
what is DOM?
(Documnet object model) reprents the web page as a tree like sturtuer, 
     which alloews js. 
     to dynamically access and manipulsation
     the content and struture of a web page.
    1. BRower takes HTML and create DOM.
    2.Js helps us modify DOM based on user actions or events.
    [html DOM banat hai CSS usi DOM sunder 
    Javascript kya kisi chij ko delete karta hai,
    hide karta hai, show katea hai add karta hai
    to js Dom ko bar bar manupulate karte rahte hai.]

Real DOM- agra esme kuch add kate hai to pure UI pe impact hoga 
          to pure loyout re-render karega to slow kam karega.
  means thora time lega.

Virtual Dom- likin app virtual dom me kuch change karte hai ya kuch add krte hai to 
             jo ak particular chij hi re-render hoga (jo app change krege)
  means ye fast kam karega.

(react ke under library hai jo bhi algoritham process hota hai Usko bolte hai Reconcliation.)


